title: Anjaana
subTitle: Raju, a garage mechanic, falls in love with Rachna but her guardian, Diwan, opposes the marriage and humiliates Raju's mother. Raju decides to exact his revenge against Diwan and teach him a lesson.

title: Aakhri Daao
subTitle: Ravi, a burglar, leaves his life of crime behind and starts afresh winning the trust and respect of the local community. His life takes a turn when his former crime partner approaches him with a job.

title: Madhosh
subTitle: Young Raya and Soni fall deeply in love and secretly marry against their families' wishes. However, as time passes, Raya begins to struggle with the challenges of life and starts mistreating Soni.

title: My Life My Story
subTitle: The host invites prominent Bollywood celebrities who open up about their personal life and share interesting anecdotes based on their experiences.

title: Bhuvan Shome
subTitle: A lonely bureaucrat goes on holiday to a village in Gujarat where a young peasant woman helps him see beyond his job and develop a newfound empathy for people.

title: Parivaar
subTitle: When a young girl is thrown out of her home by her evil relatives, she finds shelter with a poor street performer and his two children, a dog and a monkey.

title: Amba
subTitle: When Amba gets her son Rajendra arrested for sexually assaulting their servant's daughter, Rajendra's wife wreaks havoc into their lives as she vows to avenge him.

title: Dost
subTitle: Maanav befriends Gopichand, a reformed thief, and helps him secure a job to turn his life around. However, Maanav suddenly disappears and returns just in time to support Gopichand during a crisis.

title: Desh Premee
subTitle: Master Dinanath's life crumbles after he helps arrest Thakur Pratab Singh. Estranged from his wife and daughter, he relocates to a slum with his son Raju, who tragically falls into a life of crime.

title: Apna Desh
subTitle: Akash, an honest man, loses his job due to the corruption of his seniors. As he strives to get his job back and his brother is wrongly framed, he attempts to fight and prove his brother's innocence.

title: Aage Ki Soch
subTitle: Ganpat, an honest merchant, falls in love with Sapna when she visits his village with her friends. One day, she returns as a married woman, breaking Ganpat's heart.

title: Ek Shriman Ek Shrimati
subTitle: Pritam, a young man, falls for Deepali, the wealthy daughter of a rich industrialist. However, she is in love with Ajit and plans to marry him but Pritam tries to woo her and win her over.

title: Dulhan Wahi Jo Piya Man Bhaaye
subTitle: Prem is in a fix when his grandfather demands to meet his lover, Rita. When Prem pays a street florist to masquerade as Rita, the old man quickly gets attached to the caring girl.

title: Dastaan-E-Rafi
subTitle: Renowned celebrities discuss the life journey of gifted singer Mohammed Rafi, sharing moments and incidents they experienced with him during his career.

title: Pyar Mohabbat
subTitle: Prince Naresh Kumar Singh runs away from home and returns to his kingdom after 18 years with a new identity. However, he realises that his family is in shambles and a stranger is to be crowned king.

title: Jaag Utha Insan
subTitle: Mahant Chaturvedi did not approve of his daughter marrying outside of their caste to Gopi, and as such breaks off all relations with them. Years later, Gopi attempts to make amends by bringing his group.

title: Rajput
subTitle: Janaki, a young woman, loves Manu Pratap Singh but is forced to marry Dhirendra, a police inspector. However, when she gets kidnapped by a man, who tries to rape her, Manu saves her in time.

title: Khilona Bana Khalnayak
subTitle: Tatya Vinchu, a dying gangster, transfer his soul into a doll. The ventriloquist Lakshya unknowingly brings the sinister doll into his life, leading to chaos.

title: Naseeb
subTitle: The lives of friends Namdev, Raghu, Damu and Jaggi take a turn for the worse when they win a lottery. Raghu and Damu murder Jaggi and frame Namdev who later returns to seek revenge.

title: Gautam Govinda
subTitle: Gautam, a dedicated officer, is transferred to a town that is teeming with criminals and ruled by Dharamdutt. In order to tackle Gautam, Dharamdutt sends his most able and trusted man, Govinda.

title: Gautam Govinda

title: Kunwara Baap
subTitle: A rickshaw driver's life changes when he finds an abandoned baby at his doorstep. When the child is affected by polio, he has a change of heart and decides to care for him.

title: Saaransh
subTitle: When Pradhan and Parvati lose their son, they open their home to Sujata Suman, a struggling actress. Her presence brings comfort and renewed hope to the mourning parents.

title: Bahurani
subTitle: Amit wants to marry a modern woman but his parents get him married to a village girl, Madhuri. When Amit refuses to accept her as his wife, Madhuri reinvents herself as Malathi and re-enters his life.

title: Sitara
subTitle: The life of a couple who shifts to Mumbai to prepare for their marriage, undergoes a drastic change when the lady becomes a popular movie star overnight and forgets her purpose amidst the glamour.

title: Jheel Ke Us Paar
subTitle: Sameer falls in love with Neelu, a girl with visual impairment, and plans to restore her sight. However, his mother disapproves of their union and hatches a plot to break them apart.

title: Kuchhe Dhaage
subTitle: To avenge his father's death, Lakhan kills Roopa's father, Tulsiram, in cold blood. Enraged, Roopa decides to kill him, but fate has its own plans.

title: Do Chor
subTitle: Tony, a burglar, comes under the radar of suspicion when a series of mysterious thefts bewilder the police. Soon enough, he tries to redeem his honour by going after the real criminal.

title: Dacait
subTitle: After being mercilessly beaten and abandoned to die, a young man is rescued by a band of dacoits, who nurse him back to health in their hidden lair.

title: Dosti Dushmani
subTitle: Sandeep, Ranjit and Prakash are best friends from childhood. A misunderstanding between Ranjit and Sandeep leads the former to believe that the latter is a criminal.
